window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jason is learning more about his powers to Godhood. Throw a Dungeon and its core into the mix, and things get even more interesting....</b></p> <p>He'll need to deal with Temples now, but not in the way he expected. Michael, his wives, and a few others are embarking on something that might change the course of the cosmos themselves. Add in the Elves from Earth and their story about travelling across the stars and the thrills will just keep coming.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>This book contains harem themes, adult language, and some monster girls.</i></p>"; 
